    "description": "S-Pool, Inc. provides business and human resources solutions in Japan. The company offers part-time and temporary employment recruitment; face-to-face member acquisition; and consulting services for calculating greenhouse gas emissions, disclosing environmental information, and carbon offset intermediation. It also provides temporary staffing; office support staffing for call centers; in-store sales support staffing for smartphones and home appliances; human resources services for the hotel industry; and field consulting services. In addition, the company offers special needs employment services, human resource outsourcing services, professional human resources utilization services, sales promotion support services, cybersecurity services, environmental management support services, decarbonization support services for local authorities, logistics outsourcing services, employment support services, wide-area administrative BPO services, business succession support services, cross-border e-commerce and marketing support services, and sales support services for municipal governments. Further, it leases farms suitable for employment for people with disabilities; and operates shared warehouses. S-Pool, Inc. was incorporated in 1999 and is headquartered in Chiyoda, Japan."
